obj_root_law:
  slug the-police-forces-restriction-of-rights-act-1966
  handle (1704)
  collectionHandle 123456789/1362
  title `The Police-Forces (Restriction of Rights) Act, 1966`
  actNumber (33)
  enactmentDate 1966-12-02
  sourceUrl `https://www.indiacode.nic.in/handle/123456789/1704`
  sources obj_root_law_sources
  sections obj_root_law_sections
  hindiTitle `पुलिस बल (अधिकारों का निर्बन्‍धन) अधिनियम, 1966`
  actYear (1966)
  ministry `Ministry of Home Affairs`
  department `Department of Internal Security`
  longTitle `An Act to provide for the restriction of certain rights conferred by Part III of the Constitution in their application to the members of the Forces charged with the maintenance of public order so as to ensure the proper discharge of their duties and the maintenance of discipline among them.`
  enforcementDate 03-12-1966
  notification `3rd December, 1966, vide notification No. G.S.R. 1848, dated 3rd December, 1966, in respect of the Union territory of Delhi, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, sec. 3(i). 2. 1st August, 1967, vide notification No. S.O. 1122(E), dated 20th July, 1967, in respect of the Union territories of Andaman and Nicobar Islands, Chandigarh, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, sec. 3(ii). 3. 4th September, 1967, vide Panjab Govt. notification No. S.O. 67 C. A. 33/66/S. 1/67, dated 2nd, September, 1967, in respect of the State of Panjab, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary.`
  fetchedAt `2026-05-08T23:22:07.845Z`
  translations obj_root_law_translations
